ol.li:
Customize the rendering of the document:

Create a css/main.css file.

Add some styles inside it. You can start
              with:* {
  display: block;
}

/** Display the element name before each element. This rule is useful only for development. */
*:before(1001) {
  content: oxy_name() " ";
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-family: monospace;
  background-color: lightgray;
}
